# Imported Markdown Content

[money, minorUnits](std/money.ssc)
[contentModuleSection](std/content.ssc)

```scalascript
val section =
  contentModuleSection(
    "std-money",
    "minor-units-integer-count-of-the-smallest-unit-e-g-cents"
  ).get

println(section.title)
println(minorUnits(money("12.34", "USD")).toString)
```

